    • printChat

      public void printChat(String username)
      The method prints the entire chat, displaying all the messages present. Each message is printed with the username of the sender. If the username matches the specified one, the displayed name will be "You".
      Parameters:
      username - the username for which you want to print the chat

    • printChatLast

      public void printChatLast(String username)
      The method prints the last message of the chat. The message is printed with the username of the sender. If the username matches the specified one, the displayed name will be "You".
      Parameters:
      username - the username for which you want to print the last message
